    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty car, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive! She's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend adventures. I\u2019ve taken great care of her, so she\u2019s ready to hit the road with you right away. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable ride that still looks sharp and drives smoothly, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love for her to go to someone who will enjoy her as much as I have! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
