    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. This example delivers a visceral driving experience through its 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is bolstered by proactive subframe reinforcement, addressing a known E46 weak point, while the suspension retains its original geometry for precise turn-in. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the powertrain remains robust with a linear power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline. A technically sound platform for the purist valuing mechanical feedback and analog performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
