    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of a well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior maintains a deep, glossy finish with only the minor, inevitable stone chips consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium upholstery remains supple, and all electronic features\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the intuitive navigation system\u2014function exactly as they should. Mechanically, the car is in robust health, benefiting from a consistent service history and recent fluid changes. It starts reliably, shifts smoothly, and offers a composed, quiet ride. This is a dependable, high-quality choice for a buyer looking for a turn-key vehicle that balances luxury with long-term value.",
